rs holdings corporation  beverly road  hoffman estates il     directions from ohare international airport  take i tollway west toward rockford continue approximately  miles and exit at beverly road and proceed north right turn right into sears holdings campus on sears parkway you will see the sears holdings sign marking the entrance go straight at the stop sign pass under the main entrance and park in the visitor lot ahead  directions from midway airport  take cicero avenue north turn right onto the ramp for i n stevenson expressway to chicago take the ryan expyi wi w exit a to wisconsin keep following signs be sure to stay on i w as it splits near montrose and continue  miles past ohare airport pass route  and exit at beverly road proceed north right for less than a mile turn right into sears holdings campus on sears parkway you will see the sears holdings sign marking the entrance go straight at the stop sign pass under the main entrance and park in the visitor lot ahead overview awards  recognitions business opportunities our culture government affairs sears about sears sears history kmart about kmart kmart history corporate timeline multicultural initiatives product recalls brands sears kmart shop your way kenmore diehard sears auto center sears home services  sears brands llc investors  sears holdings corporation close search bar search mobile navigation sears holdings corporation investors sears holdings stock trades on the nasdaq national market under the stock symbol shld fiscal  q financial results thursday may   see press release download press release pdf listen to webcast flash and wmv view presentation deck pdf transcript pdf details and logistics xbrl files form q may   » february  chairmans letter february   to our shareholders associates and members  has proven to be the year where the impact of the changes i have described to you in the past has spread more broadly to retailers that had previously proven to be relatively immune to such shifts walmart nordstrom macy’s staples whole foods and many others have felt the impact of disruptive changes from online competition and new business models these shifts also are affecting companies that influence where people purchase products and the specific products they choose like google and facebook as well as companies that deliver products to customers continue reading » investors home events  presentations annual reports chairmans letters financial transactions xbrl files legal notice corporate governance board of directors senior management team corporate governance guidelines code of conduct board committees audit committee charter compensation committee charter finance committee charter nominating committee charter code of conduct for the board of directors us securities and exchange commission sec filings section  filings transfer agent for stock  account records computershare trust company na po box  college station tx  tel  computersharecom  sears brands llc about us  sears holdings corporation close search bar search mobile navigation sears holdings corporation overview sears holdings corporation nasdaq shld is a leading integrated retailer focused on seamlessly connecting the digital and physical shopping experiences to serve our members  wherever whenever and however they want to shop sears holdings is home to shop your way® a social shopping platform offering members rewards for shopping at sears and kmart as well as with other retail partners across categories important to them the company operates through its subsidiaries including sears roebuck and co and kmart corporation with fullline and specialty retail stores across the united states overview awards  recognitions business opportunities our culture government affairs sears about sears sears history kmart about kmart kmart history corporate timeline multicultural initiatives product recalls brands sears kmart shop your way kenmore diehard sears auto center sears home services  sears brands llc kmart  