that customers can now simply ask alexa to interact with their kenmore smart appliances said charlie kindel director of alexa smart home the partnership however comes amid sears massive struggle to compete with online retailers the announcement did have a positive effect causing sears holdings corps shares to jump more than  percent as it makes a last ditch effort to win back customers according to multiple reports the retailer said the move is part of its multifaceted strategy to support the brands growth said tom park president of kenmore craftsman and diehard brands at sears holdings in the statement  edward s lampert chairman and ceo of sears holdings said in the statement that the launch of kenmore products on amazoncom would significantly expand the distribution and availability of the kenmore brand in the us the retailer however has been continuing to bleed money shutter stores throughout the country and layoff employees earlier this year sears which also operates kmart raised significant doubts of its ability to continue previous reports said the company has closed more than  sears and kmart stores in the us last month sears laid off  corporate employees spencer kent may be reached at skentnjadvancemediacom follow him on twitter spencermkent find the find njcom on facebook   view comments alexa can you help save sears retailer to sell kenmore products on amazon  njcom njcom back to main menu close customize your weather set your location enter city and state or zip code congratulations your weather is set to  you can change the location at any time accuweathercom quick look change your current location » view full weather report search search njcom account sign in close sign in tonjcom you are signed in as edit public profile sign out subscribe email newsletters the starledger the times of trenton the jersey journal south jersey times hunterdon county democrat alexa can you help save sears retailer to sell kenmore products on amazon comment updated on july  