amed as one of the best places to work for lgbt equality published by the human rights campaign for  controversyedit havas mediaedit kmart was the target of an industrial workers of the world iww campaign in  to get the company to stop advertising with havas media called media planning group at the time in  havas media laid off  of their  us employees approximately  despite the company posting increasing profits the iww accused havas media of putting extra money in their pockets and called for kmart to stop using havas media until a fair severance package for the terminated employees could be negotiated to put further pressure on kmart the union protested outside of kmart stores including one store located on astor place in manhattan sears holdings has not commented publicly about the matter see alsoedit chicago portal companies portal sears kmart kmart australia sears canada sears mexico in the matter of sears holdings management corporation referencesedit  a b c d e f g h i j k  form k sears holding company pdf sears holdings   barbash fred barbaro michael november   sears kmart to merge in b deal the washington post retrieved may     a b c document wwwsecgov retrieved    sears future may include slimmed down stores chicago tribune retrieved     national retail federation  are sears canadas days numbered poor results could have us retailers circling soon    businessweek  sears holdings press releases searsholdingscom retrieved    sears may have eye on safeway chicago suntimes  risky side of sears retailer is recast as a hedge fund as sales and stores decline chairman focuses on investment the washington post march    the new alchemy at sears businessweek april   retrieved  august    sears takes  stake in restoration hardware finanznachrichtende  much marylin march   sears updates its online marketplace servicelivecom investors business daily retrieved april     sears starts auto center franchise program february   retrieved february     twin titanics or turnaround