 it sponsored the  gillett evernham motorsports car of scott riggs for the september   running of the sharp aquos  at california speedway through its sears auto center branch however riggs failed to qualify for the event in  craftsman became the title sponsor of the world racing group world of outlaws sprint car racing series diversityedit the company received a  rating on the  corporate equality index published by the human rights campaign for the seventh year in a row it was named one of the  best companies for working mothers in  by working mothers magazine the company was named as one of the best places to work for lgbt equality published by the human rights campaign for  controversyedit havas mediaedit kmart was the target of an industrial workers of the world iww campaign in  to get the company to stop advertising with havas media called media planning group at the time in  havas media laid off  of their  us employees approximately  despite the company posting increasing profits the iww accused havas media of putting extra money in their pockets and called for kmart to stop using havas media until a fair severance package for the terminated employees could be negotiated to put further pressure on kmart the union protested outside of kmart stores including one store located on astor place in manhattan sears holdings has not commented publicly about the matter see alsoedit chicago portal companies portal sears kmart kmart australia sears canada sears mexico in the matter of sears holdings management corporation referencesedit  a b c d e f g h i j k  form k sears holding company pdf sears holdings   barbash fred barbaro michael november   sears kmart to merge in b deal the washington post retrieved may     a b c document wwwsecgov retrieved    sears future may include slimmed down stores chicago tribune retrieved     national retail federation  are sears canadas days numbered poor results could have us retailers circling soon    businessweek  sears holdings press